short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search all your watched videos on YouTube

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YT-engine allows the user to index their Youtube history, and utilize it in the website to search for keyword or phrases. 
Keeping track of watched videos is required for this app to work.
